  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个图，展示把 main 分支合并到未开发分支的过程。方向用从上到下（top to bottom），标题写 \"Merge from main onto undeveloped branch (top-to-bottom)\"",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "gitGraph TB",
        "main",
        "undeveloped"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，\"undeveloped\" 是指 develop 分支吗？还是另一个独立的分支？另外，合并方向是 main 合并进 develop，还是 develop 合并进 main？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "develop",
        "undeveloped",
        "merge direction"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，undeveloped 就是 develop 分支。合并方向是 main 合并进 develop，也就是 develop 接收 main 的更新。先有一个初始 commit，然后从 main 切出 develop 分支。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit",
        "branch develop",
        "main",
        "merge main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出基础结构：初始 commit，然后从 main checkout 出来切到 develop 分支，develop 上再做一个 commit。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "commit",
        "branch develop",
        "checkout main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来需要回到 main 分支做一个 commit，模拟 main 上有新进展，然后再切回 develop 分支执行 merge。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout main",
        "commit",
        "checkout develop",
        "merge main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：checkout 回 main，做一个 commit，然后 checkout 到 develop，最后执行 merge main。这样 develop 就合并了 main 的最新改动。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "checkout main",
        "commit",
        "checkout develop",
        "merge main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "检查一下，develop 分支上的 commit 是在切出之后、合并之前对吧？时间线应该是：初始 commit → 切 develop → develop commit → 回 main commit → 回 develop merge main。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
        "commit order",
        "merge main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认无误。develop 上的独立 commit 在合并前，main 的 commit 在 checkout main 之后，最后用 merge main 把 main 的更新整合进 develop。图已经完整了。",
